article.description: Florida A&M defeated Johnson University 103-71 on Friday night.
article.headline: Florida A&M defeats Johnson 103-71
article.story:
TALLAHASSEE, Fla. --  Florida A&M defeated Johnson University 103-71 on Friday night.

The Rattlers lost 23 straight games last year in finishing 2-27 but notched an easy victory in their season opener against the Suns (2-2) of the National Christian College Athletic Association.
